      • playMatch

        void playMatch(Match match)
        The match maker will process and play the game of the given match. Then it will clean up the match from the matched list and move it to the completed list. Then, the match maker will release all players so they can be matched to another game.
        Parameters:
        match - - The match to be played

      • playMatches

        void playMatches()
        The match maker processes (play the games of) all the currently completed match ups. Then it will clean up all the matches from the matched list and move them to the completed list. Then, the match maker will release all players so they can be matched to another game
